<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>About this program:</h2>
        <p>This is an in-store video rental program that allows users (customer representatives) 
        to rent out videos (DVDs) and check them back in. There's also administrator's mode which grants more 
        permissions to manage the application.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Features:</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Built using ASP.Net Core 2.1</li>
            <li>RESTful Services built with ASP.NET Web API</li>
            <li>Data Models are build using Entity Framework Code-First pattern</li>
            <li>Client side uses jQuery, AJAX and such plugins like DataTables</li>
            <li>Authentication with OAuth and social logins (Facebook and Google)</li>
            <li>The application supports Administrator features and User features</li>
            <li>The website is deployed on Azure</li>
            <li>The database used is MSSQL</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
